some guards around my father's room.

261
00:26:01,766 --> 00:26:03,654
Phil, take him in.

262
00:26:03,768 --> 00:26:06,100
The kid's clean, Captain.
He's a war hero.

263
00:26:06,204 --> 00:26:09,093
- He's never been busted-
- Goddamn it, I said take him in.

264
00:26:11,209 --> 00:26:13,734
What's the Turk paying you
to set up my father, Captain?

265
00:26:15,046 --> 00:26:17,071
Take ahold of him.
Stand him up.

266
00:26:17,181 --> 00:26:19,206
Stand him up straight.

267
