hired to protect Vito Corleone.

269
00:26:47,245 --> 00:26:48,906
They're licensed to carry
firearms.

270
00:26:49,013 --> 00:26:51,504
If you interfere, you'll have to
appear before a judge...

271
00:26:51,582 --> 00:26:54,142
in the morning
and show cause.

272
00:26:54,252 --> 00:26:56,743
