276
00:27:32,623 --> 00:27:35,251
After the hospital thing,
Sonny got mad.

277
00:27:35,359 --> 00:27:38,487
We hit Bruno Tattaglia
at 4:00 this morning.

278
00:27:39,797 --> 00:27:41,196
Jesus Christ.

279
