Just beautiful.

284
00:28:12,129 --> 00:28:13,528
You're gorgeous.

285
00:28:13,631 --> 00:28:16,327
Hey, listen to this.
The Turk, he wants to talk.

286
00:28:16,434 --> 00:28:19,164
