facing me.

466
00:39:17,094 --> 00:39:19,983
I guess I'm getting
too old for my job.

467
00:39:21,098 --> 00:39:23,054
Too grouchy.

468
00:39:23,166 --> 00:39:25,828
Can't stand the aggravation.

469
00:39:25,936 --> 00:39:27,301
You know how it is.

470
00:39:29,272 --> 00:39:30,705
He's clean.

471
00:39:57,634 --> 00:39:59,659
We're going to Jersey?

472
00:40:01,805 --> 00:40:03,102
Maybe.

473
00:40:28,932 --> 00:40:30,422
Nice work, Lou.

474
00:41:08,105 --> 00:41:10,061
How's the Italian food
in this restaurant?

475
00:41:10,173 --> 00:41:12,505
Good.
Try the veal.

476
00:41:12,609 --> 00:41:14,600
- It's the best in the city.
- I'll have it.

477
00:41:51,114 --> 00:41:52,877
I'm gonna speak Italian
to Mike.

478
00:41:52,983 --> 00:41:54,382
Go ahead.

479
00:43:13,897 --> 00:43:15,296
What I want-

480
00:43:16,566 --> 00:43:18,454
what's most important to me-

481
00:43:21,404 --> 00:43:23,463
is that I have a guarantee:

482
00:43:23,573 --> 00:43:25,632
no more attempts
on my father's life.

483
00:43:25,742 --> 00:43:29,974
What guarantees could I give you?
I am the hunted one.

484
00:43:30,580 --> 00:43:33,640
I missed my chance.
